OL,3,CLancashire health trust criticised
OL,4,Cover baby death got thousands for
OL,5,C'safe' care
OL,7,FA NHS health trust in Lancashire which
OL,8,Fwas criticised by a coroner for a
OL,9,Fstring of failures leading to the
OL,10,Fdeath of a baby girl was paid #730,000
OL,11,Ffor 'safe' maternity care in the same
OL,12,Fyear, it has been revealed.
OL,14,FIda Lock died in November 2019 from a
OL,15,Fserious brain injury, days after she
OL,16,Fwas born at Royal Lancaster Infirmary.
