OL,3,CLancashire health trust criticised
OL,4,Cover baby death got thousands for
OL,5,C'safe' care
OL,7,FA senior coroner concluded on Friday
OL,8,F21 March that Ida died from a lack of
OL,9,Foxygen during her delivery at the
OL,10,Fhospital because midwives did not
OL,11,Fprovide basic medical care.
OL,13,FHM Senior Coroner for Lancashire Dr
OL,14,FJames Adeley said Ida's death was
OL,15,Fcontributed to by the lead midwife's
OL,16,F"wholly incompetent failure" to give
OL,17,Fbasic neonatal resuscitation.
OL,19,FHe also also identified eight missed
OL,20,Fopportunities by midwives to alter the
OL,21,Finfant's clinical course.
