OL,5,C'safe' care
OL,7,FIn 2019, University Hospitals of
OL,8,FMorecambe Bay NHS Foundation Trust
OL,9,F(UHMBT), which runs Royal Lancaster
OL,10,FInfirmary, received #734,112 under the
OL,11,FMaternity Incentive Scheme run by NHS
OL,12,FResolution, the health service's
OL,13,Finsurance arm.
OL,15,FThe scheme offers a financial
OL,16,Fincentive to improve maternity safety
OL,17,Fwithin NHS trusts if they meet
OL,18,Frequirements in 10 areas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
