OL,3,CLancashire health trust criticised
OL,4,Cover baby death got thousands for
OL,5,C'safe' care
OL,7,FUHMBT reported it had met all the
OL,8,Fscheme's key safety actions in 2019
OL,9,Fand received the payout, but later had
OL,10,Fto repay most of it after a critical
OL,11,Freport of its maternity services by
OL,12,Finspectors from the Care Quality
OL,13,FCommission.
OL,15,FThe trust was the subject of a damning
OL,16,Freport in 2015 that found a "lethal
OL,17,Fmix" of problems at another of its
OL,18,Fmaternity units at Furness General
OL,19,FHospital that led to the unnecessary
OL,20,Fdeaths of 11 babies and one mother
OL,21,Fbetween 2004 and 2013.
