OL,7,FThe Morecambe Bay investigation,
OL,8,Fchaired by Dr Bill Kirkup, uncovered a
OL,9,Fseries of failures "at every level"
OL,10,Ffrom the unit to those responsible for
OL,11,Fregulating and monitoring the trust.
OL,13,FIda's inquest at County Hall, Preston,
OL,14,Frevealed similar shortcomings in
OL,15,Fclinical governance that were
OL,16,Funcovered in Dr Kirkup's inquiry.
