OL,7,FFollowing the hearing, her parents
OL,8,FRyan Lock and Sarah Robinson, from
OL,9,FMorecambe, criticised UHMBT for a lack
OL,10,Fof candour about the care of their
OL,11,Fdaughter and said it should not be "a
OL,12,Ftest of endurance for bereaved and
OL,13,Fbewildered parents" to work out what
OL,14,Fhappened to their child.
